high_descs: Turn right, go half way across the room and turn right to the counter with two knives.
Pick up the knife that is not on the edge.
Turn around and head to the fridge.
Cut the potato in the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the counter.
Put the knife on the counter to the left of the other knife.
Turn around and head back to the fridge.
Pick up a slice of potato from the fridge.
Turn right and head to the microwave above the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn right and go back to the counter with the knives.
Put the slice of potato on top of the knife on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight slightly then turn right and walk to the kitchen counter
Pick up the butter knife from the counter
Turn around and walk straight to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door and slice the potato on the shelf then close the door
Turn around and walk straight to the kitchen counter
Place the butter knife on the counter
Turn around and walk straight to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door and pick up a slice of potato the close the door
Turn around walk straight slightly then turn left and walk to the microwave
Place the potato slice in the microwave and heat it then remove it from the microwave
Turn around and walk straight slightly then turn left and face the kitchen counter with the butter knives
Place the potato slice on the counter next to the knife
anns.task_desc: Heat or cook a potato slice in the microwave

high_descs: Go to the kitchen counter
Pick up a butterknife from the counter
Go to the fridge
Cut a potato in the fridge
Go to the counter
Place the butterknife back on the counter
Go to the fridge
Pick up a potato slice from the fridge
Go to the microwave
Heat a potato slice in the microwave
Go to the counter
Place the potato slice next to the butterknife
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato slice on a kitchen counter
